<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 01:48:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>脑肿瘤和免疫细胞之间的动态相互作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/dynamic-interactions-between-brain-tumors-and-immune-cells</link><description>胶质母细胞瘤是成人中最常见和最具侵袭性的脑肿瘤类型，仍然难以治疗，因为它可以浸润周围的脑组织并远远超出主要肿瘤。研究人员利用先进的显微镜捕捉到了活体大脑中的这种渗透过程。他们的研究基于对患有与人类胶质母细胞瘤非常相似的脑癌的小鼠的观察。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/dynamic-interactions-between-brain-tumors-and-immune-cells2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 01:48:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/dynamic-interactions-between-brain-tumors-and-immune-cells</guid></item><item><title>伊恩·麦吉尔克里斯特——意识和死后生命？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/iain-mcgilchrist-consciousness-and-life-after-death</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 01:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/iain-mcgilchrist-consciousness-and-life-after-death</guid></item><item><title>动物园假说</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-zoo-hypothesis</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 01:18:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/the-zoo-hypothesis</guid></item><item><title>天然激素可以逆转肥胖吗？新研究揭晓答案</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/could-a-natural-hormone-reverse-obesity-new-research-reveals-the-answer</link><description>在一项开创性的研究中，科学家解开了肥胖难题的一个重要部分，发现一种天然存在的激素可以通过与 Ozempic 和 Wegovy 等流行减肥药物相同的大脑控制中心来逆转体重增加。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/could-a-natural-hormone-reverse-obesity-new-research-reveals-the-answer.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 01:03:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/could-a-natural-hormone-reverse-obesity-new-research-reveals-the-answer</guid></item><item><title>堆叠智能表面可以提高 6G 的无线可靠性和安全性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/stacked-intelligent-surfaces-could-boost-wireless-reliability-and-security-for-6g</link><description>得益于 UBC Okanagan 研究人员的新想法，无线通信将变得更强大、更清晰、更安全。工程学院的 Anas Chaaban 博士和他的团队正在探索一种方法，以改进堆叠智能表面 (SIS) 更有效地处理电磁波的方式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/stacked-intelligent-surfaces-could-boost-wireless-reliability-and-security-for-6g.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 00:48:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/stacked-intelligent-surfaces-could-boost-wireless-reliability-and-security-for-6g</guid></item><item><title>“微观管理”免疫激活和蛋白质周转：健康和疾病背景下的小胶质细胞溶酶体</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/micro-managing-immune-activation-and-protein-turnover-microglial-lysosomes-in-the-context-of-health-and-disease</link><description>小胶质细胞溶酶体免疫激活和蛋白质周转。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/micro-managing-immune-activation-and-protein-turnover-microglial-lysosomes-in-the-context-of-health-and-disease2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 00:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/micro-managing-immune-activation-and-protein-turnover-microglial-lysosomes-in-the-context-of-health-and-disease</guid></item><item><title>儿童脑癌中的蛋白质相互作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/protein-interactions-in-childhood-brain-cancer</link><description>神经母细胞瘤是一种罕见的神经系统肿瘤疾病，几乎只影响儿童，主要是两岁以下的儿童。大约一半的儿童患有高危肿瘤，治愈的机会较低。 N-MYC 与神经母细胞瘤预后较差有关。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/protein-interactions-in-childhood-brain-cancer2.jpg" /&gt; 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDa